node.text: John Eggleston (@eggleston_emporium) has mastered the art of fractal-burning, a process in which 2,400 volts of electricity is applied to timber to singe beautiful fractal-patterns onto the surface. He is also running a free giveaway for a beautiful fractal-burnt serving board embellished with blue resin. Check out @eggleston_emporium and find out how to enter for your chance to win!
